Package com.fortify.pub.issueparsing

Interface BaseAnalysisFileParser

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AnalysisFileParser, AnalysisSingleFileParser
    public interface BaseAnalysisFileParser
    The base interface for both zip file-based parsers (for example, FPRs) and single file-based parsers (for example, FVDLs)

        Parameters:
